<li><a href="/wiki/Tor_N%C3%B8rretranders" title="Tor Nørretranders">Tor Nørretranders</a>, author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/John_Allen_Paulos" title="John Allen Paulos">John Allen Paulos</a>, mathematician and author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Fred_Pearce" title="Fred Pearce">Fred Pearce</a>, journalist at New Scientist</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Yakov_I._Perelman" title="Yakov I. Perelman">Yakov I. Perelman</a>, author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Steven_Pinker" title="Steven Pinker">Steven Pinker</a>, experimental psychologist, cognitive scientist and author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Robert_Pollack" title="Robert Pollack">Robert Pollack</a>, biologist and author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Magnus_Pyke" title="Magnus Pyke">Magnus Pyke</a>, author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/V._S._Ramachandran" title="V. S. Ramachandran" class="mw-redirect">V. S. Ramachandran</a>, neuroscientist, cognitive scientist and author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Matt_Ridley" title="Matt Ridley">Matt Ridley</a>, zoologist, journalist and author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Steven_Rose" title="Steven Rose">Steven Rose</a>, biologist, neurobiologist, broadcaster and author</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Oliver_Sacks" title="Oliver Sacks">Oliver Sacks</a>, neurologist and author</li>
